WEBVTT

00:00.200 --> 00:01.686
Previously on "Greenleaf"...

00:01.753 --> 00:03.606
When you're the response pastor,

00:03.680 --> 00:05.780
you are the face of the
church with a capital "C."

00:05.782 --> 00:08.450
- So, how'd she look?
- She's got nothing on you.

00:08.452 --> 00:10.985
So when we start getting all upset

00:10.987 --> 00:13.388
at our friends and our parents,

00:13.390 --> 00:15.390
the one you should turn to is God.

00:15.392 --> 00:17.992
Every time we fly, it's the same thing.

00:17.994 --> 00:19.728
We just sit here for hours.

00:19.730 --> 00:21.993
Let's take a pregnancy test.

00:22.018 --> 00:25.366
- Just so we're clear, I give.
- What do you mean?

00:25.368 --> 00:27.502
- Therapy.
- Just because I don't talk

00:27.504 --> 00:29.170
doesn't mean I'm not getting
something out of it.

00:29.172 --> 00:31.372
Bishop, it is with a heavy heart

00:31.374 --> 00:34.375
that I pitch my tent across from
yours in the field of battle.

00:34.377 --> 00:36.911
You started something here, Pastor.

00:36.913 --> 00:38.313
You're gonna let me finish.

00:38.315 --> 00:40.445
Here at Calvary, we're family!

00:43.219 --> 00:46.020
Downtown Memphis
high today will be 63 degrees

00:46.022 --> 00:48.690
with showers expected to
continue throughout the week.

00:48.692 --> 00:50.792
Showers will be heavy at times...

00:50.794 --> 00:52.160
Sophia?

00:59.401 --> 01:01.302
Sophia?

